    Alpo Petfoods Inc.
    Nestle.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
    USZ  United States of America.
    CHZ  Switzerland, West Europe.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
